  // map函数[对value的每个元素应用，返回一个新的RichMap]
  override def map(value: RichMap): RichMap = {
    val bid = value.getOrElse("bid", "").toString
    val bigdataReceiveDelay = {
      try {
        value("bigdata_receive_time").asInstanceOf[Date].getTime - value("log_time").asInstanceOf[Date].getTime
      } catch {
        case _: Throwable =>
          0L
      }
    }
    val withOid = if (localCache.contains(bid)) {
      value + ("oid" -> localCache(bid))
    } else {
      value
    }
    withOid + ("bigdata_receive_delay_ms" -> bigdataReceiveDelay) + ("bigdata_time" -> new Date())
  }
